data.title: Playlost.fm
data.text:
Playlist Sampler

Click to get an aggregate playlist that draws from playlist tracks across artist, genre, and track categories.

Get a different set of tracks by running this multiple times. This tool is new, results will vary.

Note: Spotify login is required. You will be prompted to login if you haven't already.

Top Playlists

These are the playlists that frequently match with based on the categories below. Check-out each category for additional playlists.

Click the playlist to open in a new tab.
